==English==
=== Intransitive Verb ===
'''prevaricate'''
# To shift or turn from one side to the other, from the [[direct]] course, or from [[truth]]; to evade the truth; to [[waffle]] or be (intentionally) [[ambiguous]].
# To speak with [[equivocation]]; to [[shuffle]]; to [[quibble]].
# To [[collude]], as where an [[informer]] colludes with the [[defendant]], and makes a [[sham]] [[prosecution]].

[[vi:prevaricate]]